Or for the blind, daily living on household devices - educational facilities, office facilities application services.
Imagine the teacher writing notes on the blackboard in class. Blind students can also use these non-visual interfaces to understand and read what the teacher wrote.
This is extremely precious.
What I show you today is just the beginning.
Thank you very much.
